The paper focuses on the Visual Question Answering (VQA) task, which involves the integration of computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel deep neural network for VQA, which involves the integration of multiple modalities and attention mechanisms, indicating that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
